cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically scene text detection and recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing tasks, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia).
